            "name": "Description",
            "type": "section",
            "html": "Slow-witted but having a dangerous temper, red reavers are violent forces of nature. While red reavers don\u2019t seek out fights and they are rarely aggressive when not provoked, their territorial nature and tendency to misinterpret others\u2019 actions make approaching one an exceedingly dangerous proposition."
